    "Furthermore, when used for text summarization (Phillips et al., 2022), they help synthesize content and improve the student's abstraction capabilities.",
    "Their use as learning software in virtual assistants is highly relevant to flexible learning (Wang et al., 2022; Yamaoka et al., 2022).",
